Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:10.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.02,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Le Chateau de Verre!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.56,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:07.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno worked together to \Ndefeat Klaus and Hamon, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.00,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:25.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The real Licht finally made his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.79,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)}The Lives of the Village in the Sticks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.62,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find an opening with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.66,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:20.46,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.76,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.89,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.35,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.90,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mana Zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.98,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.25,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.18,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:07.01,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He blocked our attack with that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.90,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's condensing a phenomenal \Namount of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.75,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:35.18,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,That's some hole you opened up there, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.62,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You sure that was okay, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:42.19,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You sorta blasted your sword \Nand grimoire along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.43,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he can't talk just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:54.87,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That grimoire... no longer belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.39,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.88,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:07.29,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht is definitely here. \NThat's all that matters right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.39,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:21.45,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what's his problem? \NYuno's all wet now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.60,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What if I catch a cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.55,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see you, \NI'm giving it right back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.57,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Zora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.87,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,This way. The Silver Eagles' \Ncaptain is over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.13,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,They're just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.93,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.05,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ado.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.50,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.99,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.06,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't awakened yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.82,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... We'll probably just \Nhave to wait patiently
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.90,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,until he completely awakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.23,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.20,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,How about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.78,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.27,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long, everyone! \NAbout 500 years, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.00,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you all seem well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.00,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:33.51,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,To get our other friends, \Nand to destroy the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow! My whole body hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:01.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm soaked! Everything hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:01.47,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are loud when you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:04.04,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! You're making my \Nears go all stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling stupid—\Now, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.92,top,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.30,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa! I'm glad everyone's \Nokay—ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where the heck \Ndid their hideout go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.16,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,This really sucks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.17,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,but while you were asleep, it started\N heading toward the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:26.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Wait, Zora—ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.47,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You actually did come back alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.73,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Just how lucky are you, you little shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mereoleona—ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.32,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,She's still pleasantly knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness she's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.14,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like she's \Nwaking up any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.41,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,And she'd probably kill us if we woke her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.83,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness we're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mushroom guy and the Captain \Nof the Silv—ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:51.34,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the other two became our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.02,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,With my mushroom smokescreen and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:58.10,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,with Nozel's magic's mobility, \Nwe somehow made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So others also—ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.10,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Asta of the Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.80,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to escape from \Na situation that left
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.86,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,even Mereoleona unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna recover some stamina \Nwith these herbs—ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.45,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.70,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious. \NYou're not supposed to eat those raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.24,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get a tummy ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:28.18,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Asta gave these to me... \NI'll eat them, even if they're raw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.21,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Item: Eilia's Booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:40.65,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic item that explosively heightens \Nyour body's natural healing ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.37,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You lot can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can actually feel the \Npain starting to fade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:51.48,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Letting us use such a high-level magic item...\NThank you so much, Nozel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how he can see past that hair, \Nbut maybe he's not such a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:59.39,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, may all your owies... \Nfly over to that shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't send them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.53,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hurt anymore? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.47,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.83,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.46,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...a really beaten-up Kirsch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's bro! Get your butt in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.72,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still beautiful, \Neven when I'm covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:29.10,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even beautiful when I'm being healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.69,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this guy? Is he stupid, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:38.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what happened, \Nbut Luck turned into an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.94,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The fellow from the Crimson Lion Kings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.54,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The same happened to us with Klaus and Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Same with Rill and some others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:47.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They're all pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:55.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... Look at you! A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:59.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine. I'm overflowing \Nwith magic right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:03.18,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine. I'll explain it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are? I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.95,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! I'm the Wind Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.67,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,The spatial mage who should've \Nbeen on standby is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.26,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,So apparently, he also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.95,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Nozel! Captain Nozel,\N can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.46,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:25.58,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Nozel! Thank goodness! \NI finally got through to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.08,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,It's a special communication magic \Nitem that all the captains use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:33.01,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A number of our squad members \Nsuddenly went berserk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.83,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and started saying strange \Nthings like, "We're elves!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:41.97,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They have way more magic than usual! \NWe can't handle them on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.86,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, similar incidents are \Nhappening with all of the squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.85,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's something going \Non all over the kingdom—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.14,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing is happening \Nall over the kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.83,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.40,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,We are Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:05.90,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,We must save the Clover Kingdom, \Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.95,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we have to kill \Nour fellow Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.42,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,And even if we get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:21.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Luck's attacks didn't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.18,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Whoopsie. It's been so long, I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.06,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...get up close and personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how fast he was, \Nwe were able to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:37.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.36,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Luck made sure that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.23,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,He did hit me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:48.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean Luck's soul is fighting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Yuno is doing okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:54.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the others will be \Nable to regain their senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.67,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Magic Knights, are going to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Both the kingdom and our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.13,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:17.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.98,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.41,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just after those swords of light were \Nabout to fall on us, they disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.72,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then the demon's skull started shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.09,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.77,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:36.59,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.54,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.55,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,A golden... dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.83,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,No... That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.80,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.15,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying toward the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.80,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.27,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.97,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.68,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,That robe is a Magic Knight's robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.65,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Pardon me, Sir Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.53,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you humans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:43.68,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,have increased your numbers \Ntremendously in the past few centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.77,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.35,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the region where the \Nones with weakest magic reside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.05,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,And as you move toward \Nthe center of the kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.78,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,that's where the ones with the \Nmost powerful magic reside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:59.18,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you humans still \Npractice this senseless discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.47,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,He is a Magic Knight... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:04.04,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:08.41,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you weaklings are the \Nones being discriminated against now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.05,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are selfish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.68,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.16,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,We do not discriminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:22.19,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,We will bring death upon \Nall of you humans equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:28.23,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Plant Magic: \NZhovniir's Garden of Lingering Burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm completely healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did you have to strip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:41.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just checking to see \Nif all my wounds healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put your shirt \Nback on! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.61,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've completely healed, \NI'm even more beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.13,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you hadn't healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:57.57,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Her wounds have completely healed, \Nbut she still shows no sign of waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.85,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.65,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,It's disposable, so dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:08.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Well, it's super pretty, \Nso I'll just keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.86,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.53,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,We should be in the Forsaken Realm soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.87,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like some place is \Nalready being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.21,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...Hage Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:25.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's our hometown! We need to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.05,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.46,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,We have to reach the \Nroyal capital immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.88,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting the kingdom means that \Nprotecting the royal capital comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My hometown is part of this kingdom, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.83,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on going, \Nthe two of you can go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.50,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,But you two are vital in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.94,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with this quickly, then head \Nstraight to the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.15,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.48,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You may not go, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.90,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You are royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:59.24,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to come with \Nme to protect the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Together with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:06.88,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence itself is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.92,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You do not belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.27,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! I shall accompany you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:43.79,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was strange... \Nthat I had this type of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.56,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,Poisonous plants? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.17,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.78,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:56.93,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Help... me... It feels \Nlike my body is burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:03.68,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,It was so I could weed out all \Nthese pointless, unnecessary lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:07.52,main,lily,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Holy Fist of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.50,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,There are no unnecessary lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.22,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.24,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:22.31,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a few of you \Ncan use decent magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:25.50,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,Are you what the humans call nobility?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:31.67,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, {\i1}all{\i0} humans \Nare powerless before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.46,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.83,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do something so awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:41.22,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:45.47,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,but what did the people of \Nthis village ever do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.98,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We're just trying to live \Nour lives out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.47,flashback,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,S'okay! Owies, owies, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.57,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.14,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! I don't get this at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.24,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We face hardships...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.79,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know how we're going \Nto make it through the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.74,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We suffer, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.73,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Tatoes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.54,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.71,flashback,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,I love tatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.81,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Your tato dishes are delicious, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.49,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want yours, give 'em here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:15.22,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I didn't want them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.57,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm gonna eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.38,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.79,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we laugh and have dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.70,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We're living the best we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:31.44,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we should \Nmeet such a sad end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.42,italics,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:40.95,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Orphans like us, who are poor... \Naren't allowed to dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.62,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nash...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:49.32,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up right from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.58,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Possibilities exist in everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.41,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you're \Npoor or an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can become amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.66,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.38,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They can make their dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.97,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They can make everyone happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:05.78,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll prove that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.12,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,If, just if, and it's a very huge if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.68,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,If you get into the Magic Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.48,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:17.24,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in possibilities. \NI'll believe I can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.32,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,And then one day, I'll get into \Nthe Magic Knights, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.70,flashback,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:30.27,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,After we leave, you'll be \Nthe biggest brother here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.57,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you protect everyone. \NWe're counting on you, Nash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:40.18,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,True... No one should have to face a sad end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:45.13,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to eliminate \Nthe root of all sadness: humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.10,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Plant Magic: \NZhovniir's Garden of Lingering Burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:54.35,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sister! Don't you dare touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.56,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Nash! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.08,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.73,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Father! It's Asta! Asta's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.19,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:24.22,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Good job fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...Nash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.01,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno... Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.94,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us!
