Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:10.35,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kirsch's A-I-U-E-O.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:14.71,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A-I-U-E-O, "A."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:17.16,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:18.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,"I."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:21.96,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It's great (ii). I'm beautiful, \Nand it's great (ii).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.49,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,"U."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:25.50,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm beautiful (utsukushii)?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.95,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,"E."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:29.34,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Yes, I'm beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,"O."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:35.02,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm so beautiful. Oh... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:37.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd wilt like your \Nstupid cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.52,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:42.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:47.23,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll pay for putting everyone \Nin Hage Village in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:51.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NPage 102: "Two Miracles."
